#: template-parts/sections/story.php:3
msgid "Barda: Dari Nyaris Mati ke Duta Konservasi"
msgstr "Barda: From Near Death to a Conservation Ambassador"

#: template-parts/sections/story.php:4
msgid "Ditemukan dengan luka tembak di kepala, kehilangan penglihatan, dan trauma mental mendalam. Tim YIARI memberikan perawatan medis intensif dan rehabilitasi jangka panjang."
msgstr "Found with a gunshot wound to the head, vision loss, and deep trauma, Barda received intensive medical care and long-term rehabilitation from the YIARI team."

#: template-parts/sections/story.php:5
msgid "Setelah berbulan-bulan perawatan, Barda kini hidup aman di pusat rehabilitasi kami. Ia menjadi simbol harapan yang menginspirasi ribuan orang untuk melindungi satwa Indonesia."
msgstr "After months of treatment, Barda now lives safely in our rehabilitation center. He has become a symbol of hope that inspires thousands to protect Indonesia's wildlife."

